    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Boil a kettle and heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> diced chicken thigh </strong>with a pinch of <strong>pepper</strong> and cook for an initial 8 min or until browned all over</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
