    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>quick cook spaghetti </strong>to a pot with plenty of <strong>boiled water</strong>, then bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the <strong>spaghetti</strong> for 2-3 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>spaghetti</strong>, reserving a cup of the <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
